WEBVTT

00:00.289 --> 00:03.031
- Previously on "Conviction"...
- Rodney Landon?

00:03.203 --> 00:05.770
Being a hateful jackass isn't
grounds for four life sentences.

00:05.992 --> 00:09.444
But celebrating the 10th anniversary
of 9/11 by bombing a mosque is.

00:09.538 --> 00:12.164
My plan was to blow up a mosque,
not that mosque.

00:12.198 --> 00:13.999
The best way to defend this country

00:14.034 --> 00:17.536
is to eradicate all Muslims
before they eradicate us.

00:17.570 --> 00:20.539
But innocent or guilty,
Rodney Landon needs to stay in prison.

00:20.573 --> 00:23.008
A rumor started
that Landon was getting out

00:23.043 --> 00:24.476
for snitching on other inmates.

00:24.511 --> 00:26.412
A skinhead attacked him.

00:26.446 --> 00:28.380
Landon stabbed the guy with a shiv.

00:28.415 --> 00:30.682
He isn't getting out of prison
anytime soon.

00:30.717 --> 00:34.787
Bad guy stays off the street.
Sounds like a win to me.

00:36.589 --> 00:38.757
Mr. President.

00:38.792 --> 00:41.560
Part of what he loves about you
is that you're my daughter.

00:41.594 --> 00:43.562
You were raised in a political family,

00:43.596 --> 00:46.865
you have power, access,
all the things he never had.

00:46.900 --> 00:48.067
To us.

